# {{projectName}}

A Kosmic application scaffolded with database-backed auth, zod models, and migration bootstrap.

## Scripts

- npm run dev
- npm run build
- npm run start
- npm run lint
- npm run migrate

## Development

1. Copy .env.example to .env.
2. Run npm install.
3. Start Postgres locally.
4. Run npm run migrate.
5. Run npm run dev.
6. Visit /signup to create an account, then /login.

## Included Features

- Database bootstrap under src/db
- Migration file with users, sessions, entities, emails, api_keys, and audit_log
- Zod models under src/models
- Auth wiring via @kosmic/auth in src/utils/auth.ts
- Minimal auth routes under src/routes
